questions.text: All men have limits. I ignore mine.
As a man, I am flesh and blood. I can be ignored, I can be destroyed. But as a symbol, I can be incorruptible. I can be everlasting.
I am vengeance. I am the night.
I prefer to spend time alone rather than with others
I enjoy being around people and socializing
I am energized by being around others
I am energized by being alone
I find small talk to be draining
I enjoy being the center of attention
